Hey. I took 3 favorite gg maps and smashed em into 1. The basic layout is funtimes. I threw a church from churches in, modified the entrances/exits in a way that retains the layout from funtimes. One side of the map is of the dev texture style, where I added one of the buildings from jungle, then flipped it to keep symmetry for the other side. Also added the palm tree from jungle and city. All in all, I think I like it, though I haven't gotten a chance to play it yet with anyone else.

Credit for the original maps go to the respective authors. This is not all my work, I took 3 maps and combined them with some tweaks. I only take credit for the combination of the maps, and the tweakin. :P

Feel free to use, host, distribute, decompile, edit, steal credit, flame or praise this map. The only thing I require if you host it or know any servers that host it is to send me the I.P. so I can play it! levisemail1337@gmail.com.

Thanks!

gg_churches_x_final
by Jeremy "Air" Hurley



   This map was released on 5/5. I made this map over the course of 5 days on and off.

   Of course, this map is very similar to my gg_churches_x map, but this is the updated and final version. You will find all the new features that have been updated below. I planned for more features but took them out due to many reasons. Gungame maps are about fun and not so much realism or details so I took out things like elaborate background scenery and buildings, etc.



NEW FEATURES
------------

** Bomb site's items now explode!
** Environmental sounds to add realism!
** Interior high platform inside each church now destructible!
** Destructible plants on outer walls!
** More trees and other plant-life!
** AND -- A whole new area of action on the sides with a gazebo!
** Much more!


FIXED BUG:

I fixed the skybox leak/tear effect on the sides. It's 99% fixed. Not 100% but 99%. So when you download now, you'll have gg_churches_x_final_fixed -- I renamed it with "_fixed" because too many people don't know to delete the old map file if a server won't let them connect saying they have the wrong version.

OTHER NOTES:

This map is very fun and is defininitely the last I'll make of churches. It's far superior to gg_churches_x in my opinion but let me know your thoughts. Thanks guys and have fun!

As awlays, come play with me on my server:


72.26.102.140:27015

-Air

gg_chapel - a GunGame custom map

A small European chapel is invaded by Terrorists.


Features:
- Edited *.nav file so locations have names
- Small, simple map
- Level overview
- Cubemapped, lighted, etc.
- Pakratted, so there's only one file to download
- Buyzones so you can play it without the GunGame addon
- 48 total spawn points (but I don't recommend playing with that many, it's a small map)


The map was created in about 4 days, but I spent at least 4-5 hours each day working on it. One day I spent over 10 hours working on it. I have a lot of free time.


Anyways, please constructively criticize. Thank you.

This is my first ever Counter-Strike map.

It is designed around a central post, hence it's WiP name gg_central_post.
There are two rings which radiate from around this central post.
On either side of the central post there is a ladder leading from each team's spawn to the top.
There are also two walkways/bridges leading from the center to the outer ring.
In the outer ring, a ladder leads up to the bridge.

It is quite small, but can easily support 24 players, and is quite a bloodbath with this many players.
This map is designed for Gun Game, and therefore does not have any buy zones.

Second and final version of my cemetery map. Had many complaints about the darkness of the map and all the gravestone models causing lag for those with older computers. Also decided to not put a 3d skybox.. to be honest i dont like them except in a few cases. I also decided not to add ambient sound. The whole spooky theme went out the window when i brightened the map. heres whats been changed:

Map Brightened.
Outside fence replaced with wall.
4 graves removed and replaced with larger "family" gravestone and one tunnel between the spawn points.
Replaced all gravestone models with brushes.
Removed names on graves (lot of brushwork)
Removed reflection pools.
And many others i cant think of right now.

My fellow GGNuts member Elliotuk gave me some help and personally helped to optimize the map.. nodraw, visleafs, func_details etc.. You'll notice a large improvement in FPS over the previous release. So thanks Elliotuk!

Gg_cemetary

Rec Players: 12-18

Dark "spooky" feel, with 3 mausoleums located ontop of a hill in the center of the map and rows of gravestones near the spawns and on the sides of the map arranged perfectly. Theres 2 dried up reflection pools near spawn and small fountains on the sides. 
Originally I had added a 3d skybox of dead trees but i thought it took away more than it added so i removed it. Theres already enough going on i didnt want to clutter the eyes.

About the gravestones:
Me and my wife play with a lot of folk, mostly on the westcoast gun game server (69.22.180.139:27015) and a few on my gg server (69.12.100.230:27015). Lots of good peeps and i had an idea to somehow include them in a map. On each gravestone there are names from the players we regularly play with and good friends on around 64 of the gravestones and 4 people including me in the mosoleums. Was quite a task but hopefully they all enjoy it. If your name wasnt squeezed in... uh... maybe next version? lemme know.
Thanks and enjoy!
-Cheebs
